rows.label: tlk41300011_04_msg0001
rows.name:
I hear Acedia, Superbia, Invidia,
and even Luxuria have all gathered
near the World Tree.

rows.label: tlk41300011_04_msg0002
rows.name:
When I heard that, I got worried
that this might be the end of Alst.

rows.label: tlk41300011_04_msg0003
rows.name:
But seeing how business-savvy
the Nopon are, that worry was
completely dispelled.

rows.label: tlk41300011_04_msg0004
rows.name:
They just keep raking in the cash
like there's no tomorrow. Literally.

rows.label: tlk41300011_04_msg0005
rows.name: What a gutsy bunch they are.
